snippet.title: Net64 2.0 Release & Download and Guide  [REUPLOAD]
snippet.description:
[NLU'S NOTE Reupload time, I know these videos are gonna get taken down, so I reuploaded time]

Net64 is finally out! This brings many changes, new characters and a bunch of minigames for you to play together with your friends.
For more fangames, subscribe to this channel!
https://www.youtube.com/c/KazeEmanuar...

Client:
https://github.com/Tarnadas/net64plus...
Emulator:
https://mega.nz/#!aOBAlKQJ!I3D3m1Ctyc...

Capture the flag:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1T-Ei...
https://mega.nz/#!3Xpy1BLK!sdbA70oJEy...

Find people to play with:
https://discord.gg/VyashPu

(server host is bundled with the release)
